{"tid":921847,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蕭若元稱美國不會取消香港關係法　　網民：仲勁過焦土派","createTime":"2018-11-30T01:56:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-30T02:19:02.000Z","uid":160807,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e467791cc382100b3dc5e4b4f2701df475bb118a","tid":921847,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T01:56:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.winandmac.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/memehongkong-fortune-teller-siu-us-hk-policy-act.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.winandmac.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2Fmemehongkong-fortune-teller-siu-us-hk-policy-act.jpg&h=49e0109c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蕭若元不時會上網談及時事，也會談及未來的趨勢，但由於永遠都開對家，被網民稱為超級燈神。最近其中一個熱門的政治話題，就是美國會否取消香港關係法。蕭若元於日前也就此發表言論，不少網民都稱：大鑊了，因為蕭若元認為美國短期內不會取消美國與香港關係法。<br />\n<br />\n蕭若元認為香港關係法是美國如何看香港，完全是美國內政，美國隨時有機會決定。他後來談到科技，以及走私等問題，至於詳細原因他認為與時事有關，暫時不談。<br />\n<br />\n睇片<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.winandmac.com/2018/11/fortune-teller-said-hk-and-us-policy-act-wont-be-cancelled/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.winandmac.com%2F2018%2F11%2Ffortune-teller-said-hk-and-us-policy-act-wont-be-cancelled%2F&d=JxDRBE6j8SgAGaAZIKTA0f6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=f6431c7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.winandmac.com/2018/11/fortune-teller-said-hk-and-us-policy-act-wont-be-cancelled/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40e83ebc24a9dcbc5bba0e9e4f66a9d99a4670ed","tid":921847,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T02:12:21.000Z","msg":"彌賽亞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"125ae6c3f649ebabef506966c787bc1bef8fb215","tid":921847,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T02:19:02.000Z","msg":"fortune tell